The paper focuses on image retrieval, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also proposes a new method for feature learning, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper uses Bayesian perspective to derive the loss function, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
